Breadcrumb persistence is a local bincode journal stored under the existing cache root at artifacts/breadcrumbs/<corpus_key>.bin through src/cache/breadcrumb.rs and src/cache/store.rs. The rebuild loop writes and clears this file directly in-process; no daemon, coordinator, or external service is introduced.